Hello guests! My name is Dustin, and I am a Volkswagen enthusiast and collector here in the Nashua, NH area! I currently own a 1989 VW Jetta GLI 16V as well as a 1997 VW Vento VR6 imported from Japan. I spend a lot of my free time working on the cars and attending car shows. For work, I have specialized in vehicle related customer service for over 10 years. You can check out my cars dedicated instagram page @dusty_gli

My goal is to share the joy I have for driving Volkswagens and provide guests with fun, enjoyable, and reliable vehicles to meet all your transportation needs. I am committed to accommodating any requests during your trip and will always be on standby for any questions, concerns, or assistance needed. Thank you for checking out my Volkswagens, and have a safe trip!
